assets.name: assets/e9hUieeyEaO
assets.description:
Part 2 of 6
The troll boss appears

Part 3: https://vr.google.com/objects/f2q3r-XbW1Q?e=VrZandriaUiM1

I love how blocks lets me pose characters; I literally scaled the scene and stood in each character's position in order to figure out their limb positions and lengths. Hunching myself for the troll. I also found that so much expression just comes from the eyes and stance of the fighter. (I am terrible at drawing mouths)
